text: Komsomol () is a rural locality (a village) in Yangatausky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 221 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Maloyaz, 5 km from Yangatau. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Komsomol, Salavatsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
